| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2922 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b48d8ab8-c9b0-5e4c-91c5-c60ec2768316"
